{"tid":2092923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"花旗澳門賭收按年跌97%","createTime":"2020-07-03T13:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T16:56:36.000Z","uid":225931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2048217bd379b2473936dce5cf4060f16b52e294","tid":2092923,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200629/354343812086239232.jpeg/4wJihB0PELK3dY5esCGgP_BUIdv0ZWCMVpI5XlaSOV4?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200629%2F354343812086239232.jpeg%2F4wJihB0PELK3dY5esCGgP_BUIdv0ZWCMVpI5XlaSOV4%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=5d4a2d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門政府昨日已公布6月賭收，按年跌97%至7.16億澳門元。花旗發表報告，考慮到旅行限制措施將會持續實施，將澳門7月份賭收跌幅，由32%降至94%，不排除當地賭收連續4個月跌幅逾90%。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出現時中國﹑香港及澳門政府實施的限制旅遊簽證及隔離要求，加上來自內地訪客數量，及4﹑5星級酒店入住率繼續受到旅行限制影響，令博彩業務仍處於接近零水平。<br />\n<br />\n可是當粵港澳三地互認健康碼有望啟用，三地人員流動有望逐步恢復。"},{"pid":"5a5ef005a08c3b225dce8008e9c885db74a533eb","tid":2092923,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"仲有3％？"},{"pid":"b7c1bed0e7d0865c7ae345a7acc600a72bff699f","tid":2092923,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"今年幾時派錢"},{"pid":"57e3908c7b1cd8b361991ba79fa94b588d85604d","tid":2092923,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7c1bed0e7d0865c7ae345a7acc600a72bff699f","tid":2092923,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"今年幾時派錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"今年派$300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f03e55545eafe78b69dd35813900e48d35eeb75","tid":2092923,"uid":157525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 D 賭股唔識跌"},{"pid":"6221a2b0e5368c9d47681c172a0c3392b4d2339c","tid":2092923,"uid"